metadata.name: suicide_
metadata.description: I know how it feels to keep all that thoughts of uselessness, of being guilty of all mortal sins, the constant self-hatred. It doesn't just eat you, it triggers you to implement the thought "what if I don't wake up tomorrow". 25% of the profits for this art will go to help anyone who has faced or will ever face that dreaded word 'Suicide' at Hope For The Day https://www.hftd.org/
